REQUIREMENTS
============

1. GTK+ 2.2 or above. 

2. pkg-config.  

3. gcc. Any recent version whould be OK (tested: 4.1.1 on Fedora Core 5, 4.5.1 on Fedora 14). 

4. make from autoconf tools.  

5. GStreamer or MPlayer. 
   - For GStreamer, the follwoing two packages are required: gstreamer-0.10 and gstreamer-interfaces-0.10
   - For MPlayer, the binary of the non-gui version should be installed in your path and should be  named "mplayer". 


INSTALLATION
============

1. ./configure

2. make

3. (as root) make install

The binaries are called "vbsm", "vbss", "vbsc" and "vbsd". Menu entries will be installed for you.

To build an RPM file: ifter building the sources, in the top-level source directory call "make rpm"


UNINSTALL
========

make uninstall


